notes.text:
This update for jetty-minimal fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2024-8184: Fixed remote denial-of-service in ThreadLimitHandler.getRemote() (bsc#1231651).

notes.text: There exists a security vulnerability in Jetty's ThreadLimitHandler.getRemote() which can be exploited by unauthorized users to cause remote denial-of-service (DoS) attack.  By repeatedly sending crafted requests, attackers can trigger OutofMemory errors and exhaust the server's memory.
notes.title: CVE description
